( 25029, "A sad tale, that one - a wee bit embarrassin' too.$B$BMy people be know fer havin' a taste fer the ale, ya know. And I be no exception. Seems I been given more than me share of the thirst.$B$BSo I run inta ol' Budd ya see, an' he offers me all the grog I can swallow fer joinin' his crew - a move I've come to regret.$B$BOne night, after drinkin' enough grog to drop a Kodo, I was lured into followin' Budd's band o' misfits into Zul'Aman.$B$BThat be the last I recall before findin' meself in that cage.",
