( 25031, "Kraz should never have come to this place... should have known not to trust the human. A blind fool I was, $C, as are you if you follow his counsel$B$BMy son, lost for two moons, was last seen with the human, Budd. He told me I could find him behind the walls of Zul'Aman...$B$BI followed his people here, and was captured with the rest. Without your help, I was doomed to die.$B$BThank you, stranger.",
